items.short_bio:
Knot Theory: Vassiliev invariants, Heegaard Floer and Khovanov homologies, concordance group;
Symplectic geometry and low-dimensional topology: Groups of diffeomorphisms;
Braid groups, mapping class groups: Quasi-isometries, quasi-morphisms, quasi-norms;
Geometric group theory: Quasi-isometric embeddings of finitely generated groups, bi-invariant word metrics.
